---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About" description="VScalar exists to help enterprises understand complexity, connect fragmented technology data, and make better transformation decisions.">

  <section class="page-hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">About VScalar</p>
    <h1>Building intelligence systems for complex enterprise transformation</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">
      VScalar exists to help enterprises understand complexity, connect fragmented technology data,
      and make better transformation decisions.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>Why VScalar Exists</h2>
    <p class="large-text">
      Enterprises do not fail transformation programs because they cannot move servers. They struggle
      because architecture, infrastructure, applications, security, networks, operations, compliance,
      and business constraints are deeply interconnected.
    </p>
    <p class="large-text">
      VScalar was created to address this complexity through engineering discipline, enterprise
      architecture thinking, deterministic analytics, and AI-assisted reasoning.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section light">
    <h2>Current Focus</h2>
    <div class="cards">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Enterprise Architecture Assessment</h3>
        <p>Understanding complexity before transformation begins.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Infrastructure Intelligence</h3>
        <p>Connecting infrastructure, applications, cloud, network, and operations data.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Cloud Transformation</h3>
        <p>Planning migration, modernization, readiness, and execution with better insight.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Security &amp; Network Intelligence</h3>
        <p>Supporting zero-trust, connectivity, firewall, and network transformation decisions.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Operations Excellence</h3>
        <p>Improving operational visibility, reliability, automation, and AIOps readiness.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Applied AI Research</h3>
        <p>Exploring new methods for decision intelligence, knowledge systems, and enterprise transformation.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="platform">
    <h2>Our Approach</h2>
    <p>Human-led architecture. AI-accelerated engineering.</p>
    <p>
      VScalar uses deterministic analysis where accuracy, repeatability, and auditability matter.
      AI, ML, and LLM-based reasoning are applied where context, pattern recognition, summarization,
      and architecture judgment can improve decision quality.
    </p>
  </section>

</Base>
